{"tid":2428903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"德國外交部出聲明","createTime":"2021-03-02T01:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T03:11:20.000Z","uid":90601,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17ade85a321d7d8cf33599713494e2c06d9aa5f8","tid":2428903,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:53:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GermanyDiplo/status/1366348910386700288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGermanyDiplo%2Fstatus%2F1366348910386700288&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1z2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=e346e094\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGermanyDiplo%2Fstatus%2F1366348910386700288&h=e038d6eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GermanyDiplo/status/1366348910386700288</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGermanForeignOffice<br />\n@GermanyDiplo<br />\n<br />\nGermany government organization<br />\nThe mass trial under the National Security Act in #HongKong further endangers pluralism in the city. Those arrested must be released, their rights must be respected &amp; the postponed elections need to be held as soon as possible in a fair &amp; democratic manner."},{"pid":"9d710109b6f902f897f0e6f5969a6621c652af20","tid":2428903,"uid":90601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"fb German Consulate General Hong Kong <br />\n中文版<br />\n<br />\n【德國外交部就47名民主人士被控之回應 German Federal Foreign Office responds to the trial of 47 democrats】<br />\n<br />\n因《國安法》在香港進行的大規模審訊，進一步危害了香港的多元性。被捕者必須被釋放，他們的權利必須得到尊重，被延期的選舉必須盡快以公平和民主的方式舉行。"},{"pid":"fbe8916968e7dff6c9de0f56f33b82e35c7a63bf","tid":2428903,"uid":196450,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:55:51.000Z","msg":"作用同香港人係屋企念力抗爭一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12738b3d657063eab175bb320dde911f021d0228","tid":2428903,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"